metadata.name: Intree Club Alpha Card 1
metadata.description: With an Intree Club Alpha Card you can take part in creating the new social network platform Intree. With the Alpha pass you can also: Claim exclusive benefits , Access the Intree Hub, Get the Alpha version of Intree iOS, Android, Attend events & talks at Intree Club, Get a Stamp on your Intree profile contribute to a better world trough our 25% giveback program. Gain value when the company grows, get future micro-payouts, Be a part of a closed entrepreneurial community, Enjoy our Open office at Copenhagen, Denmark 1-1 sessions with entrepreneurs, Vote on company decisions, Free future airdrops like an Intree NFT character and much more.
